<h1 id="overlay-title">Mario + Rabbids Peach Burn Effect</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Princess Peach is burned by a fire attack, forcing her to run around the playing area until she puts it out.	</p>
